{"id":"errors/NG1001","title":"NG1001: Decorator argument is not an object literal\n\n裝飾器引數不是物件字面量","contents":"<h1 id=\"ng1001-decorator-argument-is-not-an-object-literal--裝飾器引數不是物件字面量\">NG1001: Decorator argument is not an object literal\n<br>\n裝飾器引數不是物件字面量<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#ng1001-decorator-argument-is-not-an-object-literal--裝飾器引數不是物件字面量\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/errors/NG1001.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">為了使 Angular 編譯器中的元資料提取更快，裝飾器 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code>、<code>@<a href=\"api/core/Pipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">Pipe</a></code>、<code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code>、<code>@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a></code> 和 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Injectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injectable</a></code> 只能接受物件字面量作為引數。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">這是 <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/30840#issuecomment-498869540\">Ivy 中的有意更改</a>，與 View Engine 相比，它對裝飾器強制執行更嚴格的引數要求。 Ivy 需要這種方法，因為它透過將表示式移到類輸出中的其他位置來編譯這些裝飾器。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To make the metadata extraction in the Angular compiler faster, the decorators <code>@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code>, <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Pipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">Pipe</a></code>, <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code>, <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a></code>, and <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Injectable\" class=\"code-anchor\">Injectable</a></code> accept only object literals as arguments.</p>\n\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">This is an <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/30840#issuecomment-498869540\">intentional change in Ivy</a>, which enforces stricter argument requirements for decorators than View Engine. Ivy requires this approach because it compiles decorators by moving the expressions into other locations in the class output.</p>\n\n\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"debugging\">\n  <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"如何排除本錯誤\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#如何排除本錯誤\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"debugging-the-error\">Debugging the error<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG1001#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">把所有宣告：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Move all declarations:</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nconst moduleDefinition = {...}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>(moduleDefinition)\nexport class AppModule {\n    constructor() {}\n}\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">移入裝飾器：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">into the decorator:</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({...})\nexport class AppModule {\n    constructor() {}\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/Injectable\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/Pipe\n - errors/NG1001#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG1001#description\n - errors/NG1001#ng1001-decorator-argument-is-not-an-object-literal--裝飾器引數不是物件字面量\n - errors/NG1001#如何排除本錯誤\n - errors/NG1001#說明\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/errors/NG1001.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/30840#issuecomment-498869540\n-->"}